    "created_at": "2015-04-19T09:04:20Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-04-19T09:04:20Z",
    "body": "Remember that taking the address of a dereference always produces a safe reference, so need to track that reference and disallow any use that may lead to a compile-time dereference, e.g. `1 + *&*(1337 as *const u8)` should not compile (with or without `*&`).\n",
